pageContext.claim: “So, WikiLeaks is a hoax, just like everything else. And all of those problems having to do with crime were the biggest hoax of all. It was a witch hunt. A total witch hunt. And when you saw Robert Mueller's statement, the earlier statement, and then he did a recap, he did a correction later on in the afternoon.”
pageContext.analysis: This is a flip-flop for Trump. He cited WikiLeaks regularly during the final weeks of the 2016 campaign.
